GSD.description:
mmc: sdio: fix possible resource leaks in some error paths

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.14.306 by commit 92ff03c2563c9b57a027c744750f3b7d2f261c58, it was introduced in version v2.6.33 by commit 3d10a1ba0d37c8f5fd5afcdda00613fbb8a90bf5. For more details please see the references link.
